      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "POPPY'S FOX (4) got off the mark with his maiden victory last time at this track over 272m (16.02). Good beginner but will need a little luck from a middle draw. Looks the testing material. KODA MULWEE (1) has been settling off the speed lately, finishing seventh (18.23) last time in a Grade 4 at Taree Super Track. Has a good record at this journey. Safe beginner who draws ideally on the inside. Can do much better this time. ROCKIN' MIA (2) goes very well at the distance with two wins and a placing from five starts. Missed the frame latest (18.38) when sixth over 300m at Taree Super Track in a Grade 5. Looks one of the chances. MY HARLEY (3) continues to race well and is sure to be competitive again.",
